The paper deals with a SPARQL query engine, which is a database-related topic, hence cs.DB is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the use of preemption, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions experimental results, which suggests that it involves some form of machine learning or data analysis, making cs.DL a possible category. Finally, the paper proposes a new approach to SPARQL query processing, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE).
